{"tid":260313,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解化物語咁好賣","createTime":"2017-05-27T15:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T18:22:46.000Z","uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d19dbbeb8718aea40d3de63a8e5f6e8cc90c72d","tid":260313,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"我自己本身物語fans 但係傳教果陣既理由都係好唔具體<br />\n「套野好古靈精怪好得意」<br />\n「個監督種風格一鐘意就會好鐘意、唔中意就會唔知佢做乜9」<br />\n「開後宮但係唔俗、角色吸引人」<br />\n之類 但係我諗返轉頭呢類特色通常係暴死/叫好不叫座既作品特徵黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一套偏作反而會做到咁好成績 我睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n數據支持 bd top 3<br />\n<br />\n1995　203,940　14　新世紀エヴァンゲリオン<br />\n2009　110,502　*6　化物語<br />\n1979　100,350　11　機動戦士ガンダム<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cs5.pikabu.ru/images/big_size_comm_an/2014-12_6/14197705913449.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcs5.pikabu.ru%2Fimages%2Fbig_size_comm_an%2F2014-12_6%2F14197705913449.gif&h=508d2dfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9a1fce7d2f694817dc289dabf0dc2a63c48caef","tid":260313,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"有歌加乘?<br />\nnagi、仲有花澤果首好毒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事本身都幾有趣,動畫既風格將佢發揮到淋漓盡致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805cbb031a54ef9acb38540e2732e95c00a4af83","tid":260313,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"因為新房+西尾<br />\n同第12話+你所不知道的故事<br />\n造就左呢套神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429589421c67732b5f7d16d54b46837e268a4804","tid":260313,"uid":4090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6331546315951b8ac2c38294555499332dfaaed4","tid":260313,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"西尾+新房<br />\n兩個9唔塔8既一拍即合<br />\n原作粉碎機+成個故事都冇重點"},{"pid":"6b9f264ae128ae1126f47e40a609a0e64da7fd57","tid":260313,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"化物語黎講<br />\n<br />\n化物語之後應該好少 甚至無任何似佢咁癲嘅演繹方法<br />\n<br />\n連之黎嘅系列都拍唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左作畫可以再改善（但都已經係09件嘅事）<br />\n應該無乜缺點<br />\n<br />\n西尾嘅插敘<br />\n新房監督下嘅演繹<br />\n<br />\n總括而言<br />\n讀者會係睇得舒服而且故事流暢唔突兀<br />\n而且伏線令讀者驚喜 後宮都開得合理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋仲有最後一篇要買牒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f457359f7a0febd1b9c1b601dff80be86454d4f8","tid":260313,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"因為真係好好睇"},{"pid":"422686d1f0b25821f5e5fc6fc85737a443d16e70","tid":260313,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"因為得bd可以瘋狂暫停嚟睇d半秒就飛嘅字"},{"pid":"e8fa4558970769ae75de8ffeb296fa33ffd72a83","tid":260313,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為得bd可以瘋狂暫停嚟睇d半秒就飛嘅字</blockquote><br />\n笑到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a02f9449e69ffa6c42acecbfb72515865a3643","tid":260313,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為得bd可以瘋狂暫停嚟睇d半秒就飛嘅字</blockquote><br />\n笑到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中哂Point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a6508335be042749f6d0b8346379cb68e2ffa3","tid":260313,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"製作中期曾出現作畫進度無法趕及的問題，狀況可見於播放第5話後插入總集篇、第10話出現過多文字兼用卡、以至網絡話數之播放日期相差甚遠等。<span style=\"color: red;\">然而，有關狀況無阻本作牽起熱潮</span>，並創下了多項電視動畫作品之影碟銷售紀錄，同時間接束成了原作系列第二季的出現。<br />\n<br />\nwhy???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a349ed0bde2c45ba27a4e0e000678555491fa959","tid":260313,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為得bd可以瘋狂暫停嚟睇d半秒就飛嘅字</blockquote><br />\n笑到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中哂Point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最鍾意係用呢個方法表達內心想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時仲好多格字半秒飛，要係咁暫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7008ef50e62ff5d38d620fbb611712325217039","tid":260313,"uid":39413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"一開始係上網搵腹黑既女主搵搵下就搵到呢套<br />\n冇點睇內容就直接睇 睇睇下又幾好睇<br />\n神奇之處係其實好多時間都係單純人物之間既對話甚至單方面長時間既敍述但又唔會覺得悶反而又幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然好唔好睇就見仁見智 我就覺得唔錯係值得一戰既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464bb653e09d8cd2b9a726957b01e7720e1ccc68","tid":260313,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始係上網搵腹黑既女主搵搵下就搵到呢套<br />\n冇點睇內容就直接睇 睇睇下又幾好睇<br />\n神奇之處係其實好多時間都係<span style=\"color: red;\">單純人物之間既對話</span>甚至單方面長時間既敍述但又唔會覺得悶反而又幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然好唔好睇就見仁見智 我就覺得唔錯係值得一戰既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd 9up真係最愛之處<br />\n正因為咁好難憑空傳教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通話 d 9up好好睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2da2a54a5dd3317bcdea2b5f05b61dae02383b8","tid":260313,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一開始係上網搵腹黑既女主搵搵下就搵到呢套<br />\n冇點睇內容就直接睇 睇睇下又幾好睇<br />\n神奇之處係其實好多時間都係<span style=\"color: red;\">單純人物之間既對話</span>甚至單方面長時間既敍述但又唔會覺得悶反而又幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然好唔好睇就見仁見智 我就覺得唔錯係值得一戰既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd 9up真係最愛之處<br />\n正因為咁好難憑空傳教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通話 d 9up好好睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩係拎張list出黎<br />\n<br />\n千禧年代起銷量無人能及<br />\n歷史計起都係得eva勁過佢<br />\n要讚要彈首先都要睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呃人睇第一話<br />\n之後就無之後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e93edc44d506e8078373d3a32f9f3b731185207","tid":260313,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得主要因為西尾風格好夾SHAFT呢間公司<br />\n兩邊既電波對上，成套動畫自然做得好"},{"pid":"118bccaa43ceeaf20be98812f246d90fc0c61a37","tid":260313,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"雖然風格唔同，但係比故事相近既怪化貓影響左，所以唔覺得好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}